{"tid":524754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淫辱美少女 宅男自認人面獸心 官斥霸王硬上弓","createTime":"2018-01-10T02:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T07:46:27.000Z","uid":159915,"like":151,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"254b201a4672464d731f9ea585d67f0bf771f13f","tid":524754,"uid":159915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:13:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180110/20269912?_ga=2.239741381.732939120.1515392803-889528305.1509670117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F20269912%3F_ga%3D2.239741381.732939120.1515392803-889528305.1509670117&d=wbybNbZG5TiC%2FlbXGPiTWP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=08f1f050\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F20269912%3F_ga%3D2.239741381.732939120.1515392803-889528305.1509670117&h=ff778a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180110/20269912?_ga=2.239741381.732939120.1515392803-889528305.1509670117</a><br />\n<br />\n隱青因感沉悶，於凌晨時分外出散步，看見獨行夜歸20歲漂亮女大學生，遂尾隨對方返家，趁機拉她到後樓梯，壓着女生雙腿並胸襲20秒。青年早前在區域法院承認非禮罪，親撰求情信自認「人面獸心，十惡不赦」，惟心理專家評估被告不愛工作，重犯機會高於常人。法官斥被告「霸王硬上弓」，若非少女不停掙扎，隨時被強姦，判他監禁兩年。<br />\n<br />\n另外，求情階段曾出現一段小插曲，辯方大狀稱被告的女友及同事均有到庭，被告在他們支持下將可返回正軌。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">惟法官、法庭書記甚至懲教人員環視四周，公眾席上空無一人。大狀於求情尾聲回眸一看，才驚呼：「咦！點解冇人嘅？」</span>陳官亦表示剛才一直沒人。最終律師到庭外找回女友及同事。<br />\n<br />\n毒撚FF有女撐場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c3d8aebf15c96a0639a61da8e7a01aeac4c477","tid":524754,"uid":24131,"like":120,"dislike":1,"score":119,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"咦！點解冇人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 